			<li><br>Managing Attendance<br>
					<ul>
							<li>Visit the Attendance section to see who’s been present or absent.</li>
							<li>Admins can add new students and update attendance records from the Admin Dashboard.</li>
					</ul>
			</li>
			<li><br>Viewing the Schedule<br>
					<ul>
							<li>The Schedule section shows the class timetable.</li>
							<li>Admins can add or change schedule details using the Admin Dashboard.</li>
					</ul>
			</li>
			<li><br>Admin Features<br>
					<ul>
							<li>Login: Click on Admin to log in with your admin password and access special features.</li>
							<li>Add Announcements: Post new announcements about homework, events, or reminders.</li>
							<li>Update Attendance: Add new students and mark attendance for different days.</li>
							<li>Manage Schedule: Add or adjust class times and sessions.</li>
					</ul>
			</li>
			<li><br>Logging Out<br>
					<ul>
							<li>To log out, click the Logout link in the admin section.</li>
					</ul>
			</li>
			<li><br>Helpful Tips<br>
					<ul>
							<li>Keep your admin password safe and secure.</li>
							<li>Regularly update announcements and attendance for accuracy.</li>
							<li>Use the schedule to keep track of all your class timings.</li>
					</ul>
